<p>Next, it <em>shouldn't</em> happen, but just in case, if <code>$data</code> is null, that means Stripe
sent us invalid JSON. Shame on you Stripe! Throw an exception in this case... and
make sure you spell <code>Exception</code> correctly!</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="dfd8e346db">
